      "author_association" : "MEMBER",
      "body" : "Concept ACK. I was hesitant to propose this across the codebase, as some reviewers prefered kB to kvB when I was working on the initial sat/vB `fee_rate` changes. A further possibility would be to replace \"fee\" with \"fee rate\" where the meaning is a fee rate and not a fee (credit to @Xekyo for tuning my antennae to this).",
